overview_description.description: Airline Mechanical Co., Ltd. specializes in the manufacturing of power electronics with a rich history spanning over 50 years. The company focuses on producing a wide range of power supply solutions, including AC/DC switch mode power supply adaptors suitable for various applications such as set-top boxes, portable DVDs, ADSL modems, radios, gaming devices, and small home appliances. With a commitment to innovation and quality, Airline Mechanical Co., Ltd. serves a diverse clientele, aiming to meet the evolving needs of the power electronics industry.
